lead_paragraph: Kris Letang scored two goals, including the winner on a power play in overtime, to lift the Pittsburgh Penguins over the Florida Panthers 3-2 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Letang, Crosby Lead Penguins' Comeback Win Against Panthers
